<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
  .student-report {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 30px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 24px;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #555;
  }
	.course {
		width: 320px;
		height: 180px;
		color: black;
		background-color: #aeaeae;
		font-size: 24px;
	}
	#suggested-courses {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-around;
	}
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="student-report">
    <h1 style="text-align: center;">Student Report</h1>
    <div id="skill-chart"></div>
    <div>
      <h3>&bull; Communication</h3>
      <p>Your kid was exceptionally good at expressing their thoughts and ideas to the teacher and following teacherâ€™s instructions , exhibiting great communication skills.</p>
      <h3>&bull; Creativity</h3>
      <p>Your kid did assigned tasks and solved class activities in record time by creatively working on solutions, exhibiting amazing creativity.</p>
      <h3>&bull; Critical Thinking</h3>
      <p>Your kid was deeply focused and solution-oriented in class and worked dedicatedly towards finding solutions, exhibiting logical and critical thinking skills.</p>
      <h3>&bull; Collaboration</h3>
      <p>Your kid was extremely deliberate and methodical in in-class problem solving and worked well in collaboration with the teacher towards successful session, exhibiting collaboration skills.</p>
		</div>
		<h2 style="text-align: center;">Below are suggested courses for your child</h2>
		<div id="suggested-courses">
			<div class="course">HTML & CSS</div>
			<div class="course">Python</div>
		</div>
  </div>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://www.gstatic.com/charts/loader.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    google.charts.load('current', {'packages':['corechart']});
    google.charts.setOnLoadCallback(drawChart);
    var rating = <%= studentRating %>;
    function drawChart() {
			var data = new google.visualization.DataTable();
			data.addColumn('string', 'Skill');
			data.addColumn('number', 'Rating');
			data.addRows(studentRating);
			var options = {
				height: 300,
				title: 'Your Kid\'s Progress on 21st Century Skills',
				colors: ['#348ceb'],
				hAxis: {
					format: 'percent',
					ticks: [0, .2, .4, .6, .8, 1]
				},
				legend: {position: 'none'}
			};
			var chart = new google.visualization.BarChart(document.getElementById('skill-chart'));
			chart.draw(data, options);
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
